# PR checklist

- [ ] Code builds locally (or in CI) for affected packages
- [ ] Tests added/updated and passing
- [ ] Lint/format applied
- [ ] No secrets committed; env vars documented
- [ ] User-facing changes have release notes / docs updates
- [ ] Any migrations/rollout steps documented
